Can you apply this animation to our "Working..." loader .animate-shine {
  background: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground) 50%, transparent) 0%,
    var(--foreground) 50%,
    color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground) 50%, transparent) 100%
  );
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  background-clip: text;
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  animation: shine 2s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes shine {
  0% {
    background-position: 200% 0%;
  }
  100% {
    background-position: -200% 0%;
  }
}

